claim.claim-text:
1. A method of awarding a player a reward in a gaming environment, said award separate from any award received as a direct result of the outcome of a game, comprising: 
generating an account associated with said player; 
determining the satisfaction of a criteria entitling the player to an award; 
generating game play credit information comprising said award; 
associating information with said player's account regarding said award; 
permitting said player to utilize said game play credit information to play one or more games without additional monetary input.

7. A method of awarding a player an award in a gaming environment, said award separate from any award directly resulting from the play of a game comprising: 
generating an account associated with said player; 
associating information with said account, said information comprising a number of elements, said elements in one or more predetermined numbers entitling said player to an award provided by a third-party provider.

12. A method of enticing a player to play a game at a casino comprising: 
establishing an account; 
associating a plurality of credit with the account; 
generating a media, said media having information associated therewith which identifies the account; 
issuing said media to a recipient; and 
permitting said recipient to utilize said media to establish entitlement to play one or more games at said casino for free.
